                      LTGOLD and LTPRO

     The following additions have been added to your  version
of  LTGOLD  and  LTPRO.  The  switches  show  a number at the
beginning (IE:  3.1 C:\LTGOLD\LTGOLD -BW).  Do  not  use  the
number  (3.1)  in  the  command line.  It is only there as an
Index   number.   If   you   are   running   LTPRO,   replace
C:\LTGOLD\LTGOLD with C:\LTGOLD\LTPRO.

                          1.0 INDEX

1.0 INDEX                                                  1

2.0 TRANSLITERATION                                        1

3.0 BLACK AND WHITE MONITORS                               2
